1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
♪For all our days to come♪

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
♪Holding you close♪

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
♪Would that be enough?♪

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,779
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,780 --> 00:01:01,595
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,650 --> 00:01:03,682
=Episode 9=

17
00:01:27,859 --> 00:01:31,220
Song Zhiyun, you lied to me again.

18
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:44,299
Come with me.

19
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:04,299
Sir.

20
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,500
How is the plan?

21
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,900
She was taken away by Shanguan Yu.

22
00:02:13,779 --> 00:02:15,220
Take them back.

23
00:02:16,059 --> 00:02:17,220
I will find her.

24
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:22,340
Commander Gu.

25
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:27,139
There is an urgent matter to discuss.

26
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:28,979
May we speak in private?

27
00:02:30,659 --> 00:02:31,699
Grand Commandant Gao.

28
00:02:31,939 --> 00:02:33,218
The situation is pressing.

29
00:02:33,219 --> 00:02:34,419
We will discuss it tomorrow.

30
00:02:35,779 --> 00:02:37,299
Your late mother

31
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:39,460
is implicated in this case.

32
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:54,259
Song Zhiyun.

33
00:02:54,619 --> 00:02:56,379
You dare to come back?

34
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:58,900
That truly surprises me.

35
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:02,099
You have been disguised
as a man all along.

36
00:03:02,659 --> 00:03:03,580
Shanguan Yu,

37
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,259
who exactly are you?

38
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:08,539
It seems you are betting
that I will not harm you.

39
00:03:10,539 --> 00:03:12,419
But Song Zhiyun, let me tell you,

40
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:14,900
this burial ground
is filled with corpses.

41
00:03:15,539 --> 00:03:17,580
One more will make no difference.

42
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,419
You had better not act rashly.

43
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:21,379
I have already arranged men.

44
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:23,500
If I do not return within half an hour,

45
00:03:23,539 --> 00:03:24,739
that fox mask

46
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:26,732
will fall into Zhou Zihua's hands.

47
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:29,939
There are many masks
at the Shengtang Guild.

48
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:31,859
How can you be sure it is me?

49
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:33,699
So the fox was indeed you.

50
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:36,340
Look at you now.

51
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,049
In such a sorry state,
with no strength to fight back,

52
00:03:39,049 --> 00:03:41,080
and you still want
to investigate the Shengtang Guild?

53
00:03:42,425 --> 00:03:44,946
Do you really think
what you cling to is justice?

54
00:03:45,937 --> 00:03:48,782
It is nothing more
than self indulgent wishful thinking.

55
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:52,240
You cannot change anything at all.

56
00:04:01,779 --> 00:04:03,979
That night, you were wounded
on your left shoulder.

57
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,500
I remember it clearly.

58
00:04:05,779 --> 00:04:06,780
Now,

59
00:04:06,900 --> 00:04:09,460
do you still think I have
no strength to fight back?

60
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:11,500
I swear to pursue this case

61
00:04:11,779 --> 00:04:13,659
and to bring the truth to light.

62
00:04:13,779 --> 00:04:15,379
I will let everyone know

63
00:04:15,387 --> 00:04:16,778
that what you have done

64
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:18,419
is utterly disgraceful.

65
00:04:21,219 --> 00:04:22,340
What are you laughing at?

66
00:04:23,659 --> 00:04:25,260
I am laughing at you,

67
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,936
walking into danger
without even knowing it,

68
00:04:27,937 --> 00:04:30,179
reduced to a pawn
in someone else's game.

69
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:32,499
I laugh at how you
have faced life and death,

70
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:35,020
yet still have not learned caution.

71
00:04:35,179 --> 00:04:36,218
I laugh at how,

72
00:04:36,219 --> 00:04:38,619
even after losing your memory,

73
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:41,299
that stubbornness in your bones

74
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:43,220
has not diminished in the least.

75
00:04:44,675 --> 00:04:46,356
What are you talking about?

76
00:04:46,779 --> 00:04:47,979
Song Zhiyun,

77
00:04:49,339 --> 00:04:51,419
it seems you
truly have lost your memory.

78
00:04:52,287 --> 00:04:53,926
Have you forgotten

79
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:56,780
who I am as well?

80
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,619
Liu Ruyan. Ruyan.

81
00:05:32,339 --> 00:05:34,099
Liu Ruyan, listen to me.

82
00:05:35,539 --> 00:05:36,940
I cannot stay away for long.

83
00:05:37,219 --> 00:05:38,499
Go, quickly.

84
00:05:54,425 --> 00:05:55,411
You should leave.

85
00:05:55,412 --> 00:05:56,961
You have already died once.

86
00:05:56,962 --> 00:05:58,970
Do not step into danger again.

87
00:06:00,859 --> 00:06:03,099
I do not care
what we went through before,

88
00:06:03,339 --> 00:06:04,700
but why,

89
00:06:05,179 --> 00:06:06,499
why do you help me

90
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,140
and yet aid those who do wrong?

91
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:10,580
Since you are a woman,

92
00:06:10,787 --> 00:06:13,285
you should understand even more
the hardships women endure.

93
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,220
By doing this,

94
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:17,059
does your heart not ache?

95
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:18,099
Ache?

96
00:06:18,299 --> 00:06:20,659
No one knows pain better than I do.

97
00:06:22,075 --> 00:06:23,395
Because

98
00:06:24,979 --> 00:06:26,780
I was the first

99
00:06:27,299 --> 00:06:29,820
Courtesan Queen chosen
for the Shengtang Guild.

100
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:36,320
At first, I also believed that as long as I
won the title of Courtesan Queen,

101
00:06:36,350 --> 00:06:38,818
I could rise to glory.

102
00:06:39,339 --> 00:06:41,299
I thought that once I
entered the Shengtang Guild,

103
00:06:41,859 --> 00:06:43,900
better days would finally come.

104
00:06:44,099 --> 00:06:45,920
Let me out. Why are you arresting me?

105
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,739
But what awaited me

106
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:49,340
was a living hell.

107
00:06:49,739 --> 00:06:51,099
Let me out.

108
00:06:56,739 --> 00:06:59,099
I was tortured
for three days and three nights.

109
00:06:59,539 --> 00:07:01,820
I thought that if I endured it,

110
00:07:01,979 --> 00:07:03,700
I would see daylight again.

111
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:06,899
But they would not stop

112
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:09,659
until they had drained
every last bit of my worth.

113
00:07:12,339 --> 00:07:14,700
They nailed me inside a coffin

114
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:17,580
and sent me off for a ghost marriage.

115
00:07:24,299 --> 00:07:25,820
When I woke,

116
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,419
I prayed that Heaven would show mercy

117
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:29,859
and send someone to save me.

118
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:33,582
It was fortunate that you were living
at the foot of the mountain then,

119
00:07:34,175 --> 00:07:35,859
gathering herbs on the slope.

120
00:07:36,087 --> 00:07:37,527
You heard the noise

121
00:07:37,979 --> 00:07:40,179
and by chance rescued me.

122
00:07:46,739 --> 00:07:49,059
Under your meticulous care,

123
00:07:49,659 --> 00:07:51,700
my body slowly recovered.

124
00:07:52,637 --> 00:07:54,143
But my heart

125
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:57,460
remained trapped in hatred.

126
00:08:00,887 --> 00:08:03,527
Those vile men
who wronged and humiliated me,

127
00:08:03,725 --> 00:08:05,298
their faces

128
00:08:05,299 --> 00:08:07,580
would not fade from my mind.

129
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:09,459
I could not sleep at night

130
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:11,059
nor taste my food,

131
00:08:11,339 --> 00:08:13,778
because they still walked free,

132
00:08:13,779 --> 00:08:15,900
enjoying rank and wealth.

133
00:08:29,739 --> 00:08:31,579
I swore a solemn oath

134
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:32,820
to take revenge.

135
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:36,019
I trained relentlessly for three years
and returned to Huanyue House.

136
00:08:36,299 --> 00:08:37,700
I endured humiliation

137
00:08:37,779 --> 00:08:40,300
and became Zhou Zihua's executioner,

138
00:08:40,579 --> 00:08:43,820
all to seize the crucial evidence
that could bring them down.

139
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,580
Yet

140
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:50,499
fate is cruel.

141
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:52,580
Three years later,

142
00:08:52,779 --> 00:08:54,979
I encountered you again
at the Shengtang Guild.

143
00:08:56,179 --> 00:08:57,460
You

144
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:59,499
are just like I was back then,

145
00:08:59,662 --> 00:09:02,859
bewitched by
this glittering illusion of excess.

146
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:05,518
On the night
of the Courtesan Queen selection,

147
00:09:05,518 --> 00:09:07,180
I had already saved you.

148
00:09:07,912 --> 00:09:10,324
But you went back to Huanyue House

149
00:09:10,325 --> 00:09:12,207
to meet with Gu Chengye.

150
00:09:13,062 --> 00:09:15,369
In the end, you were pushed
from the upper floor.

151
00:09:15,962 --> 00:09:17,178
Because of Gu Chengye,

152
00:09:17,179 --> 00:09:18,899
you nearly lost your life.

153
00:09:18,939 --> 00:09:20,259
And what about Gu Chengye?

154
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:22,259
From beginning to end, he was using you.

155
00:09:23,037 --> 00:09:24,396
You were nothing more than

156
00:09:24,397 --> 00:09:26,877
a pawn he could discard at any time.

157
00:09:28,939 --> 00:09:30,580
Why should I believe you?

158
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:35,460
You truly are naive,
to the point of absurdity.

159
00:09:36,237 --> 00:09:38,454
Do you really think Gu Chengye
asked you to investigate

160
00:09:38,579 --> 00:09:41,660
so that he could seek justice
for those innocent people?

161
00:09:44,275 --> 00:09:46,105
Have you seen that Beauty Portrait?

162
00:09:47,459 --> 00:09:48,499
Do you know

163
00:09:49,459 --> 00:09:52,460
who the true founder
of the Shengtang Guild is?

164
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:54,899
It was Gu Chengye's mother.

165
00:09:58,812 --> 00:10:01,520
(Haitang Madam)
